The paper discusses the generation of explanations for machine learning models, which is a topic that falls under the umbrella of explainable artificial intelligence (XAI). Therefore, cs.AI is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the links between explanation-generating functions and intermediate representations of learned models, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), and cryptography (cs.CR).
